"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89a807d88e2a4475b6bacb4d339cc3a12f7076e3","tid":1570371,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:44:35.000Z","msg":"畀你買到樓又點呀？<br />\n上次選舉熱狗都提你2047年之後你擁有嘅財產都要收返畀支那人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:50:50.000Z","msg":"係佢地就唔會按撚左層樓比中資啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呃鳩 d 靚仔唔識補地價, 自己就走去按撚左層樓比中資"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"唔明你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:15:38.000Z","msg":"汪洋當年狂吹咩到期無樓, 點知佢地自己就走去按撚左自己層樓.<br />\n如果真係會無, 你就老閪都賣撚左去套現啦.<br />\n<br />\n幾乎所有業權都有到期, 到期你可以續補地價 (無錯, 你買樓係買塊地既使用權同上面既石屎.)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.landsd.gov.hk/tc/lease_ext/ext/ext2018c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.landsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Flease_ext%2Fext%2Fext2018c.pdf&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=741dabd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.landsd.gov.hk/tc/lease_ext/ext/ext2018c.pdf</a><br />\n其實香港一直有做緊續期.  當年政府已經講左就算塊契無講可以續一樣可以比地價既百份比黎租<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201609/13/P2016091300971.htm?fontSize=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201609%2F13%2FP2016091300971.htm%3FfontSize%3D1&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=60618705\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201609/13/P2016091300971.htm?fontSize=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">根據香港特別行政區政府於1997年7月公布的政策聲明，沒有續期權利的契約（不包括特殊用途契約），在期滿時可由香港特別行政區政府全權酌情決定續期50年而無須補繳地價，惟須每年繳納租金，款額相當於有關土地應課差餉租值的百分之三；租金其後亦會隨應課差餉的改變而調整。有關詳細的資料，可瀏覽地政總署網頁（<a href=\"http://www.landsd.gov.hk/tc/service/landpolicy.htm）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.landsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fservice%2Flandpolicy.htm%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=c0674903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.landsd.gov.hk/tc/service/landpolicy.htm）。</a><br />\n<br />\n自香港特別行政區成立以來，地政總署一直按上述的政策處理1997年後屆滿的契約之續期事宜，獲根據原有契約條款續期的契約無須補繳地價，但須每年繳納有關地段的地租。是否續期會考慮相關因素，包括契約屆滿時地段是否需要作公共用途或原有契約是否出現嚴重違反地契的情況等。<br />\n<br />\n現時續期或新批出的50年土地契約，年期均超越2047年。換言之，在土地行政上，2047年並不是一個期限。當然，由於大量現成的土地契約將於2047年到期，政府在適當時候需要作出安排以應對屆時岀現的大量續期工作。</span><br />\n<br />\n大陸唔係資本主義都有地賣, 咩 2047 無資本主義咩都收晒係呃鳩細路.  結果個大話穿左無人投, 佢就靜雞雞走去按左層樓.  重比人刮到層樓係低於市價一間公司名有 China 既公司轉手比佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲就更加仆街, 比人查到佢住緊層樓唔係佢既, 佢就水鳩人賣樓結果樓市繼續發癲, 信佢既就瀨晒野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/759393/page/8\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/759393/page/8</a><br />\n<br />\n所以佢日日都發夢想當選, 大拿拿成千萬可以退休."},{"pid":"a61819e29e0523d94b1e66b6e923b74625ab0c78","tid":1570371,"uid":89546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f0ff2966a8d0950610d085b0d20fc4d0faa5132","tid":1570371,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9455bf91adb12c6c58d6ad1132c9db9dd99ccbf0","tid":1570371,"uid":89546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f182e1131d23582e7f5c9f613b932118ea8c0eb7","tid":1570371,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:50:50.000Z","msg":"係佢地就唔會按撚左層樓比中資啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呃鳩 d 靚仔唔識補地價, 自己就走去按撚左層樓比中資"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"唔明你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"r