\n陳雲就更加仆街, 比人查到佢住緊層樓唔係佢既, 佢就水鳩人賣樓結果樓市繼續發癲, 信佢既就瀨晒野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/759393/page/8\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/759393/page/8</a><br />\n<br />\n所以佢日日都發夢想當選, 大拿拿成千萬可以退休."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"原來你講緊地契續期, 過左2017年之後其實已經無人提啦, 97後推/續既新地全部都係用3%應課差餉租值黎計地租, 其實已經取代左補地價續期既角色<br />\n<br />\n不過今次政府推收回土地條例就係黎真, 唔可以忽視"},{"pid":"b6ecf34633feeea51abecd0ad7480529300da245","tid":1570371,"uid":89546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"aa1f1da367e4ec3f393c3e3840d4cd8bd12489a2","tid":1570371,"uid":89546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee49e6dc23d069251664816c82322cc4c9e3b2e3","tid":1570371,"uid":89546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dba4ab7beb61edd04160ada2b49d45b32bbad71","tid":1570371,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"dhlm"},{"pid":"609a3b5966f920318d93a1d6bf958d2754dabfce","tid":1570371,"uid":89546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37124be99198333bcc5b2df3fadb2ea69a01a6ef","tid":1570371,"uid":310384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:32:09.000Z","msg":"政府原來 可以這麼有作為 之前 膽小如鼠 說收地 就說一堆 藉口<br />\n青年成功 為香港 打倒強權<br />\n<br />\n之後大家要一齊做老師 <br />\n教育下一代<br />\n要不畏強權"},{"pid":"e12182ce222e61d25abb3f6b59a270b816d8f94d","tid":1570371,"uid":89546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite